        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> I tried charming the one in the entrance of the cave a few times with about 50% chance.  CHA around 50.</P><P>Sometimes there can be two specs outside.  The tree spawn, and if someone has been playing in the cave and trained one out I have seen it hang-out for a while.  That may have been what the person saw.</P><P>Actually, two specs would rock for exp.  Fear one, kill the other while waiting for the first to come back.  If he comes back too soon, just fear him again.  One spec is a little too slow at 40+ but two would be nice.</P><P>-DV</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
